I put "kick panels" on the bottom of my doors...Made templates from the
door panels and cut them out of some scrap 1/4 inch oak faced plywood.
Rather than drill more holes in the door frames, I used plastic wall anchors
in the existing holes in the doors and screwed stainless steel roundhead
screws with ss finishing washers into the anchors...

Tony in NJ
